text.textPath: My my my.. what do we have here?
I have yet to meet one who can outsmart bullet..
So tell your mother, tell your pops, we're in a new world— it never stops!
The quick brown fox, jumped over the blue moon.
Fly high rick may, we miss you.
Didn't you see the bloody bombs!?
I am Heavy weapons guy, and this is my TANK.
